Dialogue: 0,00:00:48.66,00:00:52.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,For one moment.\nit seemed we could have peace\n在那一刻真的感觉我们可以拥有和
Dialogue: 0,00:00:54.00,00:00:55.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,=We were" so close\n我们离得如此近
