Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.66,00:01:38.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,If I catch you.\nyou are grilled meat\n要是我抓到你就把你烧成烤肉
Dialogue: 0,00:01:40.66,00:01:42.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Tara! Tara answer me!\n塔拉塔拉回答我
