Dialogue: 0,00:01:44.33,00:01:46.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,She needs energy-boosting plants\n她需要能量补充草
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.33,00:01:47.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Arpad will know which ones\n阿帕德\n知道这种草的
