Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.33,00:01:50.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,命
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.00,00:01:58.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,The barbarians\n蛮族人来了
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.66,00:01:59.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Where is your leader?\n你们的首领在哪
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.00,00:01:59.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,身
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.66,00:02:03.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I'm the leader. Pleasel\n我是求你们
Dialogue: 0,00:02:05.00,00:02:06.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Please.\n求你了
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.33,00:02:08.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,The Regent Bragan has\nalready taken almost all we had\n拉刚亲王已经征收了我们大部分粮食
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.33,00:02:12.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You lie! Tell me where\nyou have hidden your harvest\n你撒谎告诉我粮食藏在哪
Dialogue: 0,00:02:12.66,00:02:14.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,or you will regret it!\n否则你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,00:02:15.66,00:02:17.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You will be struck by bad luck!\n你会走霉运的
Dialogue: 0,00:02:18.00,00:02:20.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I have seen the signs\n我看到征兆了
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.33,00:02:23.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What you haven' t seen\nmy poor Zoldan. It's me!\n可怜的佐登你看到什么了啊是我
