Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.66,00:06:11.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Come on, Eole\n快走风神
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.00,00:06:24.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Oh, by all the devils of the sea\n以海中恶魔的名义
